"2019-10-24T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"正，支那玩佢地雙十一<br />\n我地有我地跟普世價值行"},{"pid":"3f2c7598c9cd013076501dd05eded3479982683f","tid":1671602,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:46:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中共斥巨資收賣西方<br />\n遊說集團統戰華盛頓</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=190e1f53\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=73107c35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗衡中國魔掌<br />\n組建香港既遊說團隊！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=bcebcc22\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=2803305a\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"4534c675e26f1ad1ef9fd2f7ffcdd75393a4fecb","tid":1671602,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f69aa59f06e595db602291b958f88a5d963ce2","tid":1671602,"uid":18547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"正，支那玩佢地雙十一<br />\n我地有我地跟普世價值行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T18:47:53.000Z","msg":"黑色星期五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075d26d4d3f63265cfe21cfb6e935d2e80d1c43f","tid":1671602,"uid":1